Package Model

Class Appointments

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.Appointments
  • public class Appointments
extends java.lang.Object
    The Appointments class is used as a model. When the appointment information is pulled from the data base it is held inside of appointment class objects.

        Parameters:
        appointmentID - ID for appointment
        title - String containing the title for the appointment
        description - String containing description of appointment
        location - String containing name of the location for the appointment
        type - String with name of type of appointment
        start - TimeStamp with time the appointment starts
        end - TimeStamp with the time the appointment ends
        createDate - Date of when the appointment was created
        createdBy - String with name of user that created the appointment
        lastUpdated - Date of when the appointment was last updated
        lastUpdatedBy - String with the name of the user that last updated the appointment
        customerID - int of customer id associated with appointment
        contactID - int of contact id associated with the appointment
        userID - int of the user id associated with the appointment
